<html lang="en">

  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Enquiry</title>
    <style>
      @import
      url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300&display=swap');
      * { line-height: 1.4rem; font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; font-size:
      14px; } .card { height: 100%; width: 50%; } .pt-2 { padding-top: 2px; }
    </style>
  </head>

  <body>
    <main>
      <div class="card">
        <p>Dear Admin, </p>
        <p>I hope this email finds you well. A user has Requested for an
          enquiry. Below are the details of the Enquiry:</p>
        <div>
          <span class="pt-2" style="font-weight: bold">Name:
          </span>
          <span class="pt-2">
            {{data.name}}
          </span>
        </div>
        <div>
          <span class="pt-2" style="font-weight: bold">Email:
          </span>
          <span class="pt-2">
            {{data.email}}
          </span>
        </div>
        <div>
          <span class="pt-2" style="font-weight: bold">Contact
          </span>
          <span class="pt-2">
            {{data.contact}}
          </span>
        </div>
        <p>
          Thank you for your attention to this matter.
        </p>
        <p>Best regards,<br /> Collins</p>
      </div>
    </main>
  </body>

</html>